            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <Clock size={16} strokeWidth={2.5} className="metric-icon" client:load />
            <div class="metric-content">
              <div class="metric-value">24/7</div>
              <div class="metric-label">Cobertura</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonial-tag">
          <CheckCircle size={14} strokeWidth={2.5} client:load />
          <span>Agente de Ventas</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonio 2 -->
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="quote-icon">
          <Quote size={32} strokeWidth={1.5} className="quote-svg" client:load />
        </div>
        
        <p class="testimonial-text">
          "Ahorramos <strong>15 horas por semana</strong> en gesti贸n de inventario. 
          El agente actualiza stock autom谩ticamente entre Shopify y nuestro ERP. 
          Los errores de inventario bajaron un 68%."
        </p>
        
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="author-avatar avatar-blue">
            <span>AS</span>
          </div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <div class="author-name">Ana Su谩rez</div>
            <div class="author-title">COO</div>
            <div class="author-company">Retail Plus Colombia</div>
          </div>
          <div class="author-flag"></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="testimonial-metrics">
          <div class="metric">
